      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S SAINTLY (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (30.66) in a Grade 5 at The Meadows. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. Got the money at her only try from this box. Can make amends. CRACKERJACK HOPS (3) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, rewarded with a win last time at The Meadows over 525m. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Leading chance again. JILL'S FANTASY (1) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fifth by 3 lengths (22.42). A big run wouldn't surprise. BILLY RAY MIKADO (7) generally performs well from this box.",
